Uttar Pradesh
Nov 05, 2014
Child Sexual Abuse, Rape
Description:
			A teenage girl was allegedly raped by her neighbour in Bharatpur village in Aurai area.

The incident took place on Nov 3, when the girl, aged about 14 years, was returning home. The accused R K Bind (21) dragged her to a secluded place and raped her, they said.

The family members of the girl later lodged an FIR in this regard yesterday.

Police is trying to arrest the accused, who is absconding.

